reviewText: PARTY F'N PETE. Nuff said. This show is solid gold
Too funny but  not the best one
We already had these episodes from another DVD. Not many new episodes.

This DVD contains eight episodes from the Regular Show cartoon. Amazon doesn't always do a good job on their DVD episode listings so here are the episodes that are included on this DVD:

1. Eggscellent
2. The Power
3. Ello Gov'nor
4. Cool Bikes
5. This is My Jam
6. Just Set Up the Chairs
7. Party Pete
8. Really Real Wrestling
